OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMost of the
OL,6,Fshowers dying out with clear skies for
OL,7,Fa time. Thickening cloud and patchy
OL,8,Flight rain moving into Dumfries and
OL,9,FGalloway later in the evening, pushing
OL,10,Feastwards overnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FCloudy with patchy light rain
OL,13,Fat first, mainly over the hills.
OL,14,FBrighter spells developing and feeling
OL,15,Fquite warm in any sunshine. Winds
OL,16,Flight or moderate from the southwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
